05:18.318 --> 05:22.322
I hope I will make you proud
and--

05:29.938 --> 05:34.812
It's hard.
We all miss you, and

05:34.856 --> 05:37.815
I just on keep hearing
that you are a nice--

05:37.859 --> 05:39.426
you are a nice guy.

05:39.469 --> 05:43.168
